OL,3,CWales' largest brewery announces
OL,4,Cpermanent closure of one of its bars
OL,6,FWales' largest brewery has announced
OL,7,Fplans to close one of its bars later
OL,8,Fthis month.
OL,10,FTiny Rebel confirmed its bar will shut
OL,11,Fin a social media post on Tuesday.
OL,13,FThe company blamed a drop in footfall
OL,14,Fand a "significant" increase in
OL,15,Foperating costs since for the decision.
OL,17,FIt said the move had been made
OL,18,Ffollowing "a full review," and is
OL,19,Fdesigned to make the company
OL,20,F"financially fit for the future."
