OL,3,CWales' largest brewery announces
OL,4,Cpermanent closure of one of its bars
OL,6,FThe bar on Newport High Street will
OL,7,Fclose at the end of the month, having
OL,8,Fopened as a pop-up in 2015.
OL,10,FThe centre has seen some changes in
OL,11,Fthe past few years with Newport Market
OL,12,Freopening in 2022 and a new 500-
OL,13,Fcapacity music venue opening its doors
OL,14,Flast weekend.
OL,16,FBut the brewery, which has other bars
OL,17,Fin and Rogerstone which will remain
OL,18,Fopen, said: "Since the pandemic
OL,19,FNewport city centre has been slowly
OL,20,Fimploding, with and suffering the
OL,21,Fworst."
