OL,6,FTiny Rebel also said on X, formerly
OL,7,FTwitter, the hospitality sector had
OL,8,Freceived "limited support from the
OL,9,F(Welsh) government."
OL,11,FWith other branches remaining open, it
OL,12,Fadded: "We're doing everything we can
OL,13,Fto support our staff in their next
OL,14,Fsteps, whether that's with us or an
OL,15,Fopportunity somewhere else."
