OL,3,CWales' largest brewery announces
OL,4,Cpermanent closure of one of its bars
OL,6,FReacting to the news about Tiny Rebel,
OL,7,FMS Tom Giffard, the shadow minister
OL,8,Ffor culture, tourism and sport, said:
OL,9,F"It's a damning indictment of
OL,10,Fhospitality policies that one of
OL,11,FWales' greatest recent success stories
OL,12,Fis having to scale back its presence
OL,13,Fin Newport.
OL,15,F"Tiny Rebel is a fantastic business,
OL,16,Fwith a range of popular products that
OL,17,Fare seen in bars and pubs across the
OL,18,FUK. The fact that a brand of this
OL,19,Fscale is struggling within the Welsh
OL,20,Feconomy is frankly terrifying."
