OL,6,FMr Giffard added: "Unless Labour puts
OL,7,Fin place a real strategy to keep our
OL,8,Fhospitality industry vibrant and
OL,9,Fthriving, we will find more businesses
OL,10,Flike Tiny Rebel unable to keep their
OL,11,Fdoors open."
OL,13,FA spokesperson said: "We are very
OL,14,Faware that the ongoing cost-of-living
OL,15,Fand cost-of-doing-business crises
OL,16,Fcontinues to present difficulties for
OL,17,Fsmall and independent businesses in
OL,18,Fall sectors across the country.
