OL,6,F"We are doing all we can, with the
OL,7,Fresources and powers available to us,
OL,8,Fto provide support in these difficult
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,F"We provide a range of permanent non-
OL,12,Fdomestic rates reliefs, worth #250m
OL,13,Fannually and fully funded by the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment. This includes Small
OL,15,FBusiness Rates Relief, which supports
OL,16,Fratepayers for around 70,000
OL,17,Fproperties across Wales, of which over
OL,18,F50,000 receive full relief."
