OL,6,FThe spokesperson added: "We are also
OL,7,Fproviding a fifth successive year of
OL,8,Fsupport for retail, leisure and
OL,9,Fhospitality businesses with their
OL,10,Frates bills, at a cost of #78m. This
OL,11,Fbuilds on the almost #1bn of support
OL,12,Fprovided in rates relief schemes to
OL,13,Fthese sectors since 2020-21."
OL,15,FNewport City Council has also been
OL,16,Fapproached for comment.
